{"tid":1618316,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【修例風波】多間學校指教育局下午三時將發信 消息指與反蒙面法有關","createTime":"2019-10-04T05:22:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T08:06:29.000Z","uid":215861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1a1971070070f2e60e80401fab6515d843990244","tid":1618316,"uid":215861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:22:31.000Z","msg":"2019-10-04 12:27 <br />\n<br />\n多所學校向本報證實，接獲教育局通知，今日下午3時發放重要信封給學校，要求校方「必須留意」，將內容在放學前通知所有學生，並在今日將相關訊息透過電子通訊系統、家長信等，通知全校家長。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，有關信件與政府引用《緊急情況規例條例》訂立反蒙面法有關，並對學生有所提醒，篇幅不會太長，但暫未知信件內容。<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1605511/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E5%A4%9A%E9%96%93%E5%AD%B8%E6%A0%A1%E6%8C%87%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E5%B1%80%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%88%E4%B8%89%E6%99%82%E5%B0%87%E7%99%BC%E4%BF%A1-%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%E6%8C%87%E8%88%87%E5%8F%8D%E8%92%99%E9%9D%A2%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%89%E9%97%9C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1605511%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2-%25E5%25A4%259A%25E9%2596%2593%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%2582%25B2%25E5%25B1%2580%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%2588%25E4%25B8%2589%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%25B0%2587%25E7%2599%25BC%25E4%25BF%25A1-%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%258F%258D%25E8%2592%2599%25E9%259D%25A2%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%2597%259C&d=A2ufI7QLpLp1ny1o1CjT3jXucVKzxOX0ld4zZjK7Pao%3D&h=f0fe352c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1605511%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2-%25E5%25A4%259A%25E9%2596%2593%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%2582%25B2%25E5%25B1%2580%25E4%25B8%